node.text:
Disrupt Formality

Excited to share our first Converse x DRKSHDW self shot global campaign with you all!

We want to thank our friend Rick, his team @rickowensonline and @converse for trusting our vision and giving us so much freedom to create this campaign independently!! 

We are so thrilled and happy. After everything we’ve gone through, this is truly a dream come.

Photography by Fecal Matter
Creative Direction by Fecal Matter
Makeup/Hair/Styling by Fecal Matter
Photo Assistance by @inside.voice 
Assistance by @thomasdalt

node.text:
FECAL MATTER x TRIPPEN 

We are so excited to share our shoe collaboration with the amazing @trippen.official!! 

We rarely do collabs with brands but Trippen is a really great Berlin based shoe brand that embodies a level of real authenticity when it comes to championing diversity in fashion since 1991 and really focuses on sustainability, which are core values that are really important for us. We are really excited about the collaboration as we created 2 styles of boots that really are perfect everyday shoes to provoke in for any gender expression, especially for non-binary alien beings like ourselves!! 

We are an independent emerging brand created by 2 young queer non-binary artists and all of our projects are self funded in hopes to stay true to our vision and to promote freedom of expression. The support of this project would mean everything to us! 

The boots are available to purchase right now exclusively on @trippen.official website (link in bio)!

We hope these boots act as an armour for every individual that walks through life fearlessly and offers the opportunity for all who dares to do so.

node.text:
Mutant McQueen 

A tribute to one of our favourite Lee Alexander McQueen collection titled “It’s a Jungle Out There” presented in 1997. 

McQueen’s work has inspired us deeply forever and his legacy will never die in our hearts. He was a true innovator and his unique vision  has enabled us and so many others to see beauty beyond any boundaries. This photo series is a mere gratitude project and an homage to him as we are well aware how much his beautiful work has shaped our own perspective as creators and humans.

We know he’s also a source of inspiration and a fashion hero for so many of you, so we would
love to know what are your favourite McQueen collections!!!

node.text:
It’s been a really stressful and dark past few months for us. To be honest, we are constantly feeling really overwhelmed and low. We know a lot of you feel the exact way and have also been struggling to keep it together. We don’t know when things will fully get better but we just want to send everyone reading this some love and light. It’s amazing how much Cunty helps us get through our rough moments. Spending time with her brings us so much joy. Keep prioritizing those little things that make you happy during these rough times. Thank you everyone for always checking in on us and supporting our vision, our brand and us as people.

You all have no idea how much the love means to us and how appreciative we are. WE LOVE U!!!
